  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our organization, Environmental Protection in the Caribbean (EPIC) has been  conducting environmental education, habitat restoration, and scientific research on the island of St. Maarten since 2000.  Unfortunately, Hurricane Irma has destroyed our headquarters. However, we are committed to the long-term restoration and environmental health of the island and will rebuild.  We need resources to get back on our feet and begin work as soon as possible, including replanting denuded areas.</narrative>
  </description>
